.TH DATMUX 1 "2026-01-02" "dumbass-tree" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
datmux \- tmux/screen scrollback helper (print/apply config snippets)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B datmux
[--dry-run] <command>
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B tmux
Print tmux scrollback snippet.
.TP
.B tmux --write
Append snippet to ~/.tmux.conf (with prompt).
.TP
.B screen
Print GNU screen scrollback snippet.
.TP
.B screen --write
Append snippet to ~/.screenrc (with prompt).
